name: Beginner Ballet
details: This class is designed for beginners who want to learn the fundamentals of ballet. No prior experience required.

name: Intermediate Ballet
details: Take your ballet skills to the next level with this intermediate class. Previous ballet experience recommended.

name: Advanced Ballet
details: For experienced ballet dancers who want to refine their technique and learn more advanced choreography.

name: Salsa Basics
details: Learn the basic steps and movements of salsa in this fun and energetic class. No partner required.

name: Intermediate Salsa
details: Build upon your salsa foundation and learn more complex patterns and styling.

name: Salsa Partnerwork
details: Focus on partnering techniques and improve your lead/follow skills in salsa dancing.

name: Classic Dance for Kids
details: Introduce your kids to the world of classic dance in this fun and engaging class.

name: Adult Classic Ballet
details: A classic ballet class designed specifically for adults. All skill levels welcome.

name: Hip-Hop Basics
details: Learn the basic moves and grooves of hip-hop in this high-energy class.

name: Intermediate Hip-Hop
details: Take your hip-hop skills to the next level with more complex choreography and freestyle techniques.

name: Street Dance Workshop
details: Explore various street dance styles, including popping, locking, and breaking, in this dynamic workshop.

name: Pointe Technique
details: This class focuses on developing strength and technique for dancing on pointe. Prior ballet experience and approval required.

name: Salsa Styling
details: Learn how to add flair and individual style to your salsa dancing with this styling-focused class.

name: Contemporary Dance
details: Explore the fusion of ballet and modern dance in this expressive and fluid contemporary dance class.

name: Breakdance Fundamentals
details: Master the foundational moves of breakdancing, including toprock, footwork, and power moves.

name: Jazz Fusion
details: Experience the dynamic blend of jazz and contemporary dance styles in this fusion class.
